  "name": "Nagaraja COU1 — Non-cannulated pedicle screw compression-bending credibility assessment (Minimal Profile)",
  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for FEA prediction of ASTM F1717 static compression-bending performance of a non-cannulated 7.5 mm pedicle screw construct used in lumbar spinal fusion surgery. The FEA model ensemble (FDA, Ansys, DePuy Synthes) is compared against N=11 experimental constructs across two independent laboratories. All 13 V&V 40 factors assessed; one factor (Test conditions) falls below required level due to single test condition evaluated. Intended use is pre-market submission support for Class II spinal implant, adult population, static loading regime only. Model risk level 3 per ASME V&V 40-2018 Table 1.",
  "bindsRequirement": "https://uofa.net/synth/req/nagaraja-f1717-compression-bending-req-001",
