      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Ansys Mechanical 2022 R2 and FDA in-house FEA code both hold current V&V documentation; regression test suite passes; version control enforced throughout analysis.",
      "rationale": "All three FEA platforms (FDA in-house, Ansys, DePuy Synthes) maintain ISO 9001-compliant software QA programmes with documented regression testing. Release versions used are locked and archived. Gradation 3 achieved and required for Model Risk Level 3."
    },
    {
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorType": "Numerical code verification",
      "requiredLevel": 3,
