      "achievedLevel": 3,
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Validation scenario geometry, material, loading, and boundary conditions match COU within documented similarity arguments; any differences assessed for conservatism.",
      "rationale": "Validation uses identical screw geometry, material lot, and ASTM F1717 loading as the intended regulatory submission scenario. The non-cannulated 7.5 mm configuration matches the specific device variant under assessment. Similarity argument documented; no extrapolation beyond validated envelope required for this COU. Gradation 3 met."
